snippet.title: Architect Life: A House Design Simulator | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Architect Life: A House Design Simulator will be available on June 5th, 2025!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1296400/Architect_Life_A_House_Design_Simulator/

Create dream homes! From 3D plan modelling through to on-site decision-making, you must bring each project to life while giving free rein to your creativity, to take your architectural firm to the pinnacle of the profession.

Architect Life: A House Design Simulator will be coming to Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation and PC.
